  "title": "Installer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will report for the daily Tool Box Meeting at 6am and perform site-related tasks under supervision and independently. You will manage materials, make site purchases, follow authority requirements, and support the site supervisor with various duties.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Attend the daily Tool Box Meeting at 6am to receive work instructions and safety briefings</li><li>Operate and work safely on the Gondola equipment to support site activities</li><li>Follow guidelines and instructions strictly to complete assigned tasks accurately and safely</li><li>Track and manage all materials and items on site to ensure accountability and availability</li><li>Purchase site-related materials promptly with minimal supervision to maintain workflow</li><li>Comply with all authority-related requirements during work execution and communicate with authorities when needed</li><li>Adapt to working in harsh and dusty environments while maintaining safety and productivity</li><li>Work flexible hours, including odd hours, to meet site demands</li><li>Learn quickly and perform site tasks independently as requested by the site supervisor</li><li>Carry out any additional ad-hoc duties assigned to support site operations</li></ul>",
